ipedia.org\/wiki\/Republican_Party_(United_States)\" title=\"Republican Party (United States)\">Republican<\/a> opposition for 14 months.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Peter_A._Diamond#cite_note-2\"><span>[<\/span>2<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup><\/p>","name":"Peter A. Diamond","place_of_birth":"New York, New York","place_of_death":null,"text":"Peter A. Diamond , Economics, 2010","year":2010.0}